data.description:
Completely remodeled 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home with 2 car garage and large fenced in yard! This home sits on a nice cul-de-sac while also being just minutes for everything. It boasts of its features, including 2017 roof, 2014 A/C, 2018 water heater, a new garage motor and spring in 2021, and new gutters in 2023. The home has been completely remodeled, inside and out. Just through the front door, you are welcomed with the open floor-plan consisting of the kitchen, living room, and dinning room. The Kitchen was redone in 2019 with all new cabinets, quartz counter tops, and stainless steel appliances. The flooring through the entire home was replaced in 2019 and new ceiling fans were added in 2022. The master bathroom was also just completely remodeled this year, with its dual vanity, walk in shower, free standing tub, and walk-in closet this bathroom is the perfect oasis. 
The outside of the home was fully repainted this year, windows were caulked, pavers were added to front porch, and the backyard now features a covered patio area with a fire pit all done in 2022. 

Located in the Pine Trails Subdivision this home offers privacy while being just down the road from many of the best shops, restaurants, and schools in Ormond Beach. It is move in ready and just waiting for you! Schedule a showing today!

All information recorded in the MLS intended to be accurate but cannot be guaranteed.
